                            p.aboutUs-description.pt-2.mb-0.mx-2 Al Arabi TV highlighted what inspired Foodie on a mission and how it all started all by filming during one of the recipe's shooting. Click on the video to watch this report.
            .col-12.col-sm-10.px-0
                .row.mx-0
                    .col-lg-6.col-12.mx-0.px-2.px-lg-0.mb-5
