                    .col-lg-6.col-12.mx-0.px-2.mb-5
                        .row.h-100.align-content-center.mx-2
                            p.aboutUs-Title Lebanesse representative at DOT unconference, Kenya 2018
                            p.aboutUs-description.pt-2.mb-0.mx-2  As part of Digital Opportunity Trust's Unconference 2018 in Kenya, Foodie on a mission along with 2 other social entrepreneurial initiatives were representing Lebanon. Foodie on a mission showcased the core mission, spreading awareness of our heritage, and of course, you can't talk about Lebanese food without tasting samples. 
