                .row.mx-0
                    .col-lg-6.col-12.mx-0.px-2.mb-5.embed-responsive.embed-responsive-16by9
                        iframe.w-100.embed-responsive-item( data-ux='Embed', allowfullscreen='', type='text/html', frameborder='0', src='//youtube.com/embed/gO-rI9VIk-k?rel=0&showinfo=0&start=0', data-aid='VIDEO_IFRAME_RENDERED')
                    .col-lg-6.col-12.mx-0.px-2.mb-5
                        .row.h-100.align-content-center.mx-2
                            p.aboutUs-Title Interview at the Pan-Arab morning show "Alam Al Sabah", Future TV
                            p.aboutUs-description.pt-2.mb-0.mx-2  During this interview in the tech slot, Ali Chehade highlighted Foodie on a Mission's online store that features Lebanese mouneh products. The aim was to emphasize the ease of access to traditional products instead of wandering around Lebanon to find the best mouneh makers.